spells.description:
Equip: Your damaging spells have a chance to draw a minion from the satchel, sending it running at your target where it explodes, dealing 312,940 Shadow damage split between all nearby enemies.

Damage is increased for each enemy struck, up to 5 enemies.

Equip: Your abilities have a chance to stir the sac, releasing an egg which grants you 1,241 Intellect. Each egg hatches after 1 min, and the new brood attacks your next target, inflicting 62,386 Nature damage over 8 sec.
